          h2.augmented-name 7 Questions to Angeni Kirsten Miranda

          hr.augmented-line
          .augmented-chat-holder.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/talkpush.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter")
              .arrow.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-message.talkpush Hello please tell us about your scope of responsibilities at Alorica?
          .augmented-chat-holder.left
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/angeni.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter").left
              .arrow.left
            .augmented-chat-message I am the onsite coordinator for Alorica Center (MJ Plaza). I handle 3 people of 3 different channels. I monitor their productivity and ensure that they hit their targets on a daily basis. I help in managing Talkpush leads and do callouts as well. I am also responsible with the daily and weekly reports and lastly, I do training visits and conduct talks to promote our ERP (Employee Referral Program) channel.

          hr.augmented-line
          .augmented-chat-holder.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/talkpush.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter")
              .arrow.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-message.talkpush What do you like most working in recruitment?
          .augmented-chat-holder.left
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/angeni.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter").left
              .arrow.left
            .augmented-chat-message There are a lot of things that I enjoy doing in recruitment. One is, meeting different kinds of people every day, because I get to know their personalities, their life stories and experiences (partly) and learn from what they share. Another is, of course, fulfilling the ramps and hitting the targets daily. And, It may sound crazy but I find it fulfilling when we see the applicants and employees happy knowing that we’ve served them well. In short, giving the best customer service every single day.

          hr.augmented-line
          .augmented-chat-holder.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/talkpush.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter")
              .arrow.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-message.talkpush How has technology changed the way you work since you started out in recruitment?
          .augmented-chat-holder.left
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/angeni.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter").left
              .arrow.left
            .augmented-chat-message It changed a lot. Everything became easier now because of technology. I remember getting leads manually, doing callouts manually and at the end of the day sending them SMS messages. Wow! It was really time consuming (and tiring!). Can’t imagine going back to that process. And the best change is, it saves me time! Less OTs for me!

          hr.augmented-line
          .augmented-chat-holder.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/talkpush.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter")
              .arrow.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-message.talkpush What is the future role of Artificial Intelligence in recruitment?
          .augmented-chat-holder.left
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/angeni.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter").left
              .arrow.left
            .augmented-chat-message I would say that Artificial Intelligence brings convenience not only in recruitment, but also to the applicants.

          hr.augmented-line
          .augmented-chat-holder.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/talkpush.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter")
              .arrow.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-message.talkpush What makes the recruitment process you have built different/unique?
          .augmented-chat-holder.left
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/angeni.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter").left
              .arrow.left
            .augmented-chat-message For me, what makes us different is, we use Artificial Intelligence. In just few clicks you can attract more applicants without much effort calling and texting them manually since you can do all those in the Talkpush platform. Plus, the artificial intelligence platform is interactive which makes the applicants more engaged and interested in applying. Imagine that you can upload your video when you apply. Amazing, right?

          hr.augmented-line
          .augmented-chat-holder.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/talkpush.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter")
              .arrow.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-message.talkpush Aside from Talkpush what are your other favourite tools/platforms  that you use will you recommend to your fellow augmented recruiters?
          .augmented-chat-holder.left
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/angeni.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter").left
              .arrow.left
            .augmented-chat-message Aside from Talkpush, Facebook is also one of my favorite since most people use this. It is easier to get a pool of candidates here. You can do almost everything on Facebook – recruit, post ads, pool for candidates, geo target, etc. but I think one thing that you can’t do in Facebook is to do textblast. Which brings me to another tool that I like – Netcast. Here you can send textblast with just few clicks. And if you’ve received the message, the name of our company appears which makes it more legit and convincing to the people who receives it.

          hr.augmented-line
          .augmented-chat-holder.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/talkpush.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter")
              .arrow.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-message.talkpush Enough about recruitment! What is your favourite science fiction movie of all time?
          .augmented-chat-holder.left
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/angeni.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter").left
              .arrow.left
            .augmented-chat-message STAR WARS, of course!

